### 댓글/대댓글 작성
POST http://localhost:8080/api/posts/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": 1,
  "parentId": null,
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "plain-text-password",
  "content": "새로운 댓글 내용입니다."
}

